title: The.Gods.Chain-POSTMORTEM
description:
The God's Chain
(c) CRASS Infotech

Release-Date: 08/16
Protection: Steam
Disc.Count: 1 DVD
Game.Type: Action
Language: EN

G A M E N O T E S

Finally the day came when we found our GOD. Human Beings
are an experiment done by them. The human beings are
evolving and have become one of the greatest powers in
the universe which is becoming a great problem for other
colonies in the universe. So our god decides to end the
experiment but now human beings will fight for their
existence. Will human beings exist in this space war or
will become a part of history?

Will our god destroy us or will human beings will
destroy other colonies? What will be the future of Human
Beings?
